Coding-Tuned LLM Variants Produce Version-Specific Posture Transformations — Paper License

This repository contains the source and compiled PDF of the research paper
*Coding-Tuned LLM Variants Produce Version-Specific Posture Transformations:
A Marker-Level Analysis Across Z.ai GLM and OpenAI Codex Pairs* (Tenner &
Tenner, 2026), part of the *Convergent Form, Divergent Voice II* series.

The text, tables, and figures in `paper.tex` and `paper.pdf` are
licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).

