DATA

The corpus referenced by this paper is published separately as the
*Convergent Form, Divergent Voice II — Corpus*
(Tenner & Tenner, 2026; concept DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.20013518), under its
own CC BY 4.0 license for data and MIT license for code.

